INSERT INTO market_order (
            id, 
            item_unique_name, 
            location_id, 
            quality_level, 
            enchantment_level, 
            unit_price_silver, 
            amount, 
            auction_type,
            expires_at, 
            created_at, 
            updated_at) 
        SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
            $1::BIGINT[], 
            $2::VARCHAR[], 
            $3::VARCHAR[],
            $4::INT[], 
            $5::INT[], 
            $6::INT[], 
            $7::INT[], 
            $8::VARCHAR[], 
            $9::TIMESTAMP[], 
            $10::TIMESTAMP[], 
            $11::TIMESTAMP[]) 
        ON CONFLICT (id) DO 
            UPDATE SET 
                unit_price_silver = EXCLUDED.unit_price_silver, 
                amount = EXCLUDED.amount,
                expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
                updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at
